title: How You Know It's Meant For You
description:
Hey Rehabbers:
On today's episode (119), I wanted to share a LIVE I did that really was powerful! So many people ask, "How do I know if it's meant for me?" ....I spend time talking about how I knew it was meant for me. I know this episode is going to speak to your soul! Please share it and let me know on socials how it impacted your life.
It All Starts With You.
Let's Get It.
